#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:8
#: 879b7b2c9b144d59b721f209c54947f1
msgid ""
"TG-12F模块采用平头哥TG7100C芯片，TG7100C 是智能新一代高集成 Wi-Fi 和 BLE 组合"
"芯片。无线子系统包含 2.4G 射频、Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n 和 BLE 基带/MAC 设计。微控"
"制器子系统包含一个低功耗 32 位 RISC CPU、高速缓存和存储器。电源管理单元提供灵"
"活的设置实现低功耗模式，并支持多种安全功能。"
msgstr ""
"The TG-12F module uses the T-Head TG7100C chip. TG7100C is a new-generation "
"highly integrated smart Wi-Fi and BLE combo chip. The wireless subsystem "
"includes 2.4G RF, Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n, and BLE baseband/MAC designs. The "
"microcontroller subsystem includes a low-power 32-bit RISC CPU, high-speed "
"cache, and memory. The power management unit provides flexible settings to "
"implement low-power modes and supports multiple security features."

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:10
#: 7e2f2bd00b8946df9bb7f0a7772819b0
msgid "产品特性："
msgstr "Product features:"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:12
#: 1e6d4e77b28e4cbda93d3020b1a1f67a
msgid "802.11b/g/n，Wi-Fi+BLE5.0 Combo，支持 STA，Soft AP 和 Sniffer模式"
msgstr ""
"802.11b/g/n, Wi-Fi + BLE5.0 Combo, supports STA, Soft AP, and Sniffer modes"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:13
#: 5c8d3b6bad014c439bf961e0b92ca3c5
msgid "采用开源自主可控 RISC-V CPU，1～160MHz 可调，276KB SRAM"
msgstr ""
"Uses an open-source, independently controllable RISC-V CPU, adjustable from "
"1 to 160MHz, with 276KB SRAM"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:14
#: 273dd634f3f54886bcf829601a98654f
msgid "超快连接：冷启动快连仅 70ms"
msgstr "Ultra-fast connection: cold-start quick connection in only 70ms"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:15
#: 045d609175aa4ec8a27ebc8cf9a572ae
msgid "超远距离：最大发射功率 21dBm，灵敏度-98dBm，多穿透一堵墙。"
msgstr ""
"Ultra-long range: maximum transmit power 21dBm, sensitivity -98dBm, capable "
"of penetrating one more wall"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:16
#: 78aa91cafc094f16808bccc83d2a9ab9
msgid ""
"高安全性：支持安全启动、安全调试、AES 128/192/256 加密引擎、WPA3、MD5、"
"SHA-1/224/256、PKA（RSA/ECC）加密     引擎"
msgstr ""
"High security: supports secure boot, secure debugging, AES 128/192/256 "
"encryption engine, WPA3, MD5, SHA-1/224/256, PKA (RSA/ECC) encryption engine"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:17
#: 3bc8101124b74dd2b4c530e1b725bd3b
