"IO8拉低，点击复位即可运行程序，默认波特率为921600"
msgstr ""
"After the download is completed, pull IO8 low to enter running mode, then "
"reset to run the program. In the serial port debugging assistant, checking "
"DTR can pull IO8 low. Click reset to run the program. The default baud rate "
"is 921600."
